OL,7,FA man who ran a drug line supplying
OL,8,Fcrack cocaine and heroin in Southend
OL,9,Fhas been jailed for nine years.
OL,11,FShazad Miah was arrested by police at
OL,12,FLuton airport, after returning from
OL,13,FTurkey, on 4 June 2023.
OL,15,FHe used the drug profits to fund
OL,16,F'lavish' holidays to Paris, Menorca,
OL,17,FAmsterdam and Turkey, all within four
OL,18,Fmonths.
