OL,7,FMiah held the drug line phones across
OL,8,Fa period between February and June
OL,9,F2023, with up to five runners working
OL,10,Funder him a day.
OL,12,FThe day before his arrest, he had sent
OL,13,Fpictures to one of his drug runners
OL,14,Fback in the UK on a privately
OL,15,Fchartered boat in Turkey.
