OL,7,F"He was distanced from the harsh
OL,8,Freality of crack cocaine and heroin
OL,9,Fuse, which brings associated anti-
OL,10,Fsocial behaviour impacting our
OL,11,Fcommunities and a disastrous impact on
OL,12,Fthe lives of those addicted to these
OL,13,Fsubstances.
OL,15,F"Instead, he used the profits of this
OL,16,Fdrug line to fund holidays to Paris,
OL,17,FMenorca, Amsterdam and Turkey ` all
OL,18,Fwithin a four-month period.
