OL,7,F"We traced his links to the drug line
OL,8,Fphones, we traced his financial
OL,9,Factivity and we traced his movements
OL,10,Fto build a solid case against him.
OL,12,F"He knew he faced serious prison time
OL,13,Ffor this activity, having previously
OL,14,Fbeen convicted for similar drug
OL,15,Fdealing in the past.
OL,17,F"Our work against Miah won't stop with
OL,18,Fhis imprisonment, we will be looking
OL,19,Fat ways of preventing and discouraging
OL,20,Fany further offending.
